The tool returns a dataset containing the following features:

length: Length of the message
num_links: Number of links
num_special_chars: Number of special characters
meaningful_words_percentage: Percentage of meaningful words
num_keywords: Number of keywords (specific implementation not provided in the code)
num_languages: Number of detected languages
primary_language_label: Numeric label of the primary language
primary_language_words: Number of words in the primary language
second_language_label: Numeric label of the second language
second_language_words: Number of words in the second language

Notes:

If the language cannot be detected in the message, language labels will be set to 'unknown'.
When there are no meaningful words in the message, meaningful words percentage will be set to 0.
This tool uses the langdetect library for language detection.

Author: Xinyi Chen
